Measure components: Condition [S1] Lodgement of a security : Action [27] Apply the mentioned duty : Requirement - 5.00 Tonne||Condition [S2] Lodgement of a security : Action [07] Measure not applicable : Requirement - 0.00 Tonne
Conditions: CD295: (Conditions) Eligibility for the zero import duty shall be conditional on importers lodging an import security of EUR 5 per tonne with the competent customs authorities on the day the declaration of release for free circulation is accepted (Regulation (EC) No. 2133/2001, Article 3(1) (OJ L 287)). | TM549: (Taric Measure) The customs authorities shall take representative samples of each import with a view to carrying out the necessary tests to establish that the vitreous grain content is 73|% or more. If the quality is inadequate, access to the quota shall be refused (Regulation (EC) No 2133/2001, Article 3(3) (OJ L 287)).
